data.description: Qualified buyers move in with 0 down using USDA Rural Development Loan!! Gorgeous 3 bedroom 2 bath split plan with HUGE bonus room (could be 4th bedroom with addition of closet in current attic space) is ready for new owners! Gorgeous curb appeal with professional landscaping and inviting front porch! Formal entry, formal dining, spacious living room with corner fireplace and gorgeous hardwood flooring! HUGE kitchen with granite slab counters, under cabinet lighting, gas range, plenty of cabinet and counter space and breakfast bar! Breakfast area overlooks park-like backyard! Spacious master bedroom, master bath with double vanities, Jacuzzi tub, custom tile shower and large walk in closet with plenty of built-ins! 2 spacious guest rooms and full bath on opposite side of the house. HUGE bonus room over the garage has potential of being a 4th bedroom with addition of a closet in current attic space! Wonderful privacy fenced backyard with covered patio perfect for entertaining and no backyard neighbors!!!! This property backs up to a nature area! This quiet gated community is conveniently located only minutes from Dogwood Festival Market and downtown Brandon! Excellent Brandon Schools! Call your Real Estate Professional today for your private showing!
